# Responsive Design

## ⚠️ When to Add Mobile Support

**Phone responsiveness is NOT required by default.** Only add when:
1. Explicitly requested in Jira ticket
2. Explicitly requested by user
3. Working on onboarding features
4. Component already has phone support

## Tailwind is Mobile-First

| Tailwind | useIsPhone equivalent | Applies to |
|----------|----------------------|------------|
| No prefix (base) | `isPhonePortrait === true` | Phone/mobile |
| `md:` | `isPhonePortrait === false` | Tablet and desktop |

```typescript
// Equivalent approaches:
<div className="w-full px-4 md:w-[468px] md:px-0">
<div className={isPhonePortrait ? "w-full px-4" : "w-[468px] px-0"}>
```

## Decision Framework

### Use Tailwind CSS When:
- Styling-only changes (width, padding, margins)
- Layout direction (`flex-col` → `md:flex-row`)
- Visibility (`hidden md:block`)
- Typography (`text-lg md:text-2xl`)

```typescript
// ✅ Good
<div className="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:gap-6">
<div className="hidden md:block">Desktop only</div>
```

### Use useIsPhone Hook When:
- Different components (Select on mobile vs Tabs on desktop)
- Conditional wrappers
- Different props based on device
- Structural DOM changes

```typescript
const { isPhonePortrait } = useIsPhone();

if (isPhonePortrait) {
  return <Select>...</Select>;
}
return <Tabs>...</Tabs>;

// Or different props
<DialogContent side={isPhonePortrait ? "bottom" : "right"}>
```

## Available Hooks
```typescript
import { useIsPhone } from "@/hooks/useIsPhone";
const { isPhone, isPhonePortrait, isPhoneLandscape } = useIsPhone();

import { useMediaQuery } from "@/hooks/useMediaQuery";
const isTablet = useMediaQuery("(min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px)");
```

## Breakpoints
| Prefix | Min Width |
|--------|-----------|
| `sm:` | 640px |
| `md:` | 768px |
| `lg:` | 1024px |
| `xl:` | 1280px |
| `2xl:` | 1536px |

## Why Prefer Tailwind
- No JavaScript execution
- No React re-renders
- Better initial paint (SSR friendly)
- Simpler code

Only use `useIsPhone` when CSS cannot achieve the result.
